msgid ""
"This is a complete redesign of the existing Group Rules feature. After "
"enabling this, simply go to your existing Group Rules page and you'll see an "
"entirely new, modern interface with enhanced functionality. All your "
"existing rules will be preserved. This update also adds new functionality "
"and many new group rule conditions."
